  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Preventing violence against adolescent girls in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To denounce violence against women and girls in Ghana through community-based interventions, awareness raising campaigns to address negative social norms, and working with key agencies to strengthen the response to cases of violence against women and girls. The intended beneficiaries are girls and women but the programme will work with boys and men to achieve its aims.</narrative>
  </description>
